import React from 'react'
import "./input.css"

const Input =()=> {
  return (<>
  <input className='fn' innerContent="Hello"/>
  <input className='ln'/>
  <input className='email'/>
  <input className='phone'/>
  <input className='password'/>
  <input className='confpass'/>
        
  </>)
}
export default Input;
